quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  10,31,"Bagambe (Ggwe Muhammad) nti ani abagabirira okuva mu ggulu ne mu nsi oba ani afuga okuwulira n'okulaba era ani aggya ekiramu mu kifu era n'aggya ekifu mu kiramu era ani atambuza buli kintu? Ddala bajja kukugamba nti Katonda, bagambe nti abaffe temutya"
  10,32,"Oyo nno mmwe ye Katonda Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe omutuufu. Oluvanyuma lwa mazima gano ate kiki (omuntu) kyalinda! okugyako okubula, kale nno ate muwugulwa mutya (okuva ku Katonda)"
  10,33,"Bwe kityo e kigambo kya Mukama omulabiriziwo, bwe kyakakata ku abo abaayonoona ne kiba nti mazima ddala bo tebagenda kukkiriza"
  10,34,"Gamba ggwe (Muhammad) nti abaffe mu abo bemugatta ku Katonda mulimu asobola okutandikawo ebitonde (bwamala n'abiggyawo) ate n'abizzaawo, gamba nti Katonda atandika ebitonde ate agenda kubizzaawo kale ate muwugulwa mutya"
  10,35,"Bagambe nti abaffe mu abo bemugatta ku Katonda mulimu asobola okulungamya, gamba nti Katonda alungamya eri obutuufu, yaateekwa okugobererwa oba oyo atalungamya okugyako nga alungamiziddwa mwabaaki ebintu mubisalawo mutya"
  10,36,"Abasinga obungi mu bo tebagoberera okugyako okuteeba, anti mazima okuteeba tekulina kintu kyonna kye kuyamba ku kulaga obutuufu, mazima ddala bulijjo Katonda amanyidde ddala ebyo bye bakola"
  10,37,"Kyali tekisoboka kuba nti Kur’ani eno yagunjibwawo nga teyava wa Katonda, wabula yye Katonda yagissa nga ekakasa ebyo ebitabo ebyagikulembera era nga ennyonnyola ebiri mu bitabo ebyo byonna, teriimu kubuusabuusa yava wa Mukama omulabirizi w'ebitonde byonna"
  10,38,"Oba bagamba nti (Muhammad) yagigunjaawo, gamba nti (bwemba nga nze nnagiyiiya) kale muleete essuula yonna egifaanana muyite bonna bemunaaba musobodde, nga oggyeko Katonda bwe muba nga mwogera mazima"
  10,39,"Wabula baalimbisa ebyo bye bataamanyira ddala mu bujjuvu, nga n'enzivuunula y'abyo tennabajjira bwe batyo abaabakulembera bwe baalimbisa naye tunula olabe enkomerero y'a beeyisa obubi yali etya"
  10,40,Ate mu bo mulimu abakkiriza (Kur’ani) era nga bwe mulimu abatagikkiriza era Mukama omulabiriziwo y'asinga okumanya bikwata ku boonoonyi